Updated Home screen with the recycler view having the first two letter of name and the green circular portion if the patient does not have a profile pic. Updated the action bar, above action bar theme and also included the new circular rotator in the monitor update and also in the session summary. Also updated the scan devices activity with the updated action bar. etc.. Version 2.0.4

Updates 1) Updated Home screen ->updated the battery icon made it as the cap and also reduced its size. ->Remove the battery buggs. ->included the charging symbol when the usb is connected. ->included the red battery if the battery is less than 15. ->also the battery shows disconnected and in red color if the device device is not connected. ->Session prompts if the battery is less than 15 percent. 2) Device Info Screen ->Included disconnect option in the device info screen. 3) Session Summary and Monitor Screen -> created comment section in monitor screen. ->included session number in the monitor and session summary. ->if device disconnects while in the session it asks the user to reconnect or come in range and if he comes and gets connected then session resumes normally. 4) Updated the add patient and included new feilds for the patient. 5) updated the phizio profile screen and included new feilds for phiziotherapist. 6) Removed ble connection bug( the device stays connected even after connecting to the new devicce). etc etc
temporary commit, it contains some of the utility classes to reuse some of the codes in multiple activities.
